      <title>巴基斯坦在通货膨胀加剧的情况下保持利率不变</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-29/pakistan-keeps-rates-unchanged-amid-elevated-inflation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴基斯坦央行连续第五次在会议上维持基准利率不变，当局希望在下周全国大选之前遏制亚洲最快的通胀。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-29/pakistan-keeps-rates-unchanged-amid-elevated-inflation</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 11:16:52 GMT</pubDate>
