      <title>Holcim 启动 300 亿美元分拆北美业务的计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-29/holcim-s-jenisch-considers-share-buyback-for-smooth-us-listing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞士水泥制造商 Holcim Ltd. 表示将把其北美部门分拆为一个单独的美国上市实体，此举可能会为该业务带来更高的估值，此后该公司股价上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-29/holcim-s-jenisch-considers-share-buyback-for-smooth-us-listing</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 07:45:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
